{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/4502877-midnight-sun-2008-draft", "title": "Midnight Sun [2008 Draft]", "titleComplete": "Midnight Sun [2008 Draft]", "description": "The record for the completed novel can be found here. Midnight Sun is the much anticipated retelling of Twilight from Edward Cullen's perspective. An unedited partial draft was illegally leaked onto the internet in 2008; consequently, author Stephenie Meyer put the project on indefinite hold. Shortly afterward, she posted a letter to her fans on her website including a link to the entire partial draft of the book so that those who wanted to read it could do so legally and with her consent. Note: Do not add a cover. Do not add translations. Do not add any other editions. Do not combine with editions of the full work. Do not add this book record to any series.", "genres": ["Romance", "Teen", "Fantasy", "Fiction", "Paranormal", "Paranormal Romance", "Supernatural", "Vampires", "Urban Fantasy", "Young Adult"], "author": ["Stephenie Meyer"], "publishDate": 1219906800000, "characters": ["Billy Black", "Charlie Swan", "Alice Cullen", "Jasper Hale", "Carlisle Cullen", "Edward Cullen", "Mike Newton", "Emmett Cullen", "Bella Swan", "Rosalie Hale", "Jacob Black", "Esme Cullen", "Angela Weber"], "places": ["Washington (state)", "Alaska"], "ratingHistogram": [6791, 9999, 25353, 38663, 67778], "ratingsCount": 148584, "reviewsCount": 9326, "numPages": 264, "language": "English"}
