{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6068551-shiver", "title": "Shiver", "titleComplete": "Shiver (The Wolves of Mercy Falls, #1)", "description": "For years, Grace has watched the wolves in the woods behind her house. One yellow-eyed wolf\u2014her wolf\u2014is a chilling presence she can't seem to live without.Meanwhile, Sam has lived two lives: In winter, the frozen woods, the protection of the pack, and the silent company of a fearless girl. In summer, a few precious months of being human\u2026 until the cold makes him shift back again.Now, Grace meets a yellow-eyed boy whose familiarity takes her breath away. It's her wolf. It has to be. But as winter nears, Sam must fight to stay human\u2014or risk losing himself, and Grace, forever.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1409283154i/6068551.jpg", "genres": ["Romance", "Teen", "Fantasy", "Fiction", "Paranormal", "Young Adult", "Paranormal Romance", "Supernatural", "Urban Fantasy", "Werewolves"], "asin": "0545123267", "isbn": "0545123267", "isbn13": "9780545123266", "publisher": "Scholastic Press", "series": ["The Wolves of Mercy Falls"], "author": ["Maggie Stiefvater"], "publishDate": 1230796800000, "characters": ["William Koenig", "Rachel", "Olivia Marx", "Sam  Roth", "Jack Culpeper", "Isabel Culpeper", "Grace Brisbane", "Geoffrey Beck"], "places": ["Mercy Falls, Minnesota"], "ratingHistogram": [23091, 45489, 112738, 135015, 159586], "ratingsCount": 475919, "reviewsCount": 24727, "numPages": 392, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Georgia Peach Book Award", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": "", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Pennsylvania Young Readers' Choice Award", "awardedAt": 1293868800000, "category": null, "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Children's Choice Book Award", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": "Teen Choice Book of the Year", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "Florida Teens Read", "awardedAt": 1262332800000, "category": null