{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2.Harry_Potter_and_the_Order_of_the_Phoenix", "title": "Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix", "titleComplete": "Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix (Harry Potter, #5)", "description": "Harry Potter is about to start his fifth year at Hogwarts School of Witchcraft and Wizardry. Unlike most schoolboys, Harry never enjoys his summer holidays, but this summer is even worse than usual. The Dursleys, of course, are making his life a misery, but even his best friends, Ron and Hermione, seem to be neglecting him.Harry has had enough. He is beginning to think he must do something, anything, to change his situation, when the summer holidays come to an end in a very dramatic fashion. What Harry is about to discover in his new year at Hogwarts will turn his world upside down...", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1546910265i/2.jpg", "genres": ["Classics", "Adventure", "Childrens", "Science Fiction Fantasy", "Audiobook", "Fiction", "Magic", "Young Adult Fantasy", "Middle Grade", "Young Adult"], "publisher": "Scholastic Inc.", "series": ["Harry Potter"], "author": ["J.K. Rowling", "Mary GrandPr\u00e9"], "publishDate": 1094022000000, "characters": ["Sirius Black", "Ginny Weasley", "Remus Lupin", "Cho Chang", "Kingsley Shacklebolt", "Stan Shunpike", "Rubeus Hagrid", "George Weasley", "Seamus Finnigan", "Dean Thomas", "Lucius Malfoy", "Dobby", "Dolores Umbridge", "Sybil Trelawney", "Parvati Patil", "Draco Malfoy", "Rita Skeeter", "Severus Snape", "Lord Voldemort", "Neville Longbottom", "Ron Weasley", "Harry Potter", "Vernon Dursley", "Petunia Dursley", "Padma Patil", "Pomona Sprout", "Alastor Moody", "Lavender Brown", "Kreacher", "Percy Weasley", "Dudley Dursley", "Hermione Granger", "Gilderoy Lockhart", "Luna Lovegood", "Cornelius Fudge", "Minerva McGonagall", "Fred Weasley", "Bellatrix Lestrange", "Filius Flitwick", "Molly Weasley", "Albus Dumbledore", "Nymphad